<abstract><t>An ad hoc middleware workshop was held at the International Center for Advanced Internet Research in December 1998.  The need for a more organized framework for middleware R&amp;D was recognized, and a list of specific topics needing further work was identified.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.</t></abstract>
